st often.  If I parse my logs, I do see that the number 59 occurs more than any other number.  <br><br>Also, the damage bonus is also the minimum hit.  So if you are gonna fight an uber mob you might get minimum hits a lot.  In that case, just evaluate damage bonus over delay.<br><br> - Rilkar <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uluthair.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Luthair</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1779<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/19/02 12:28:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=247.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Damage Calculator question</span><hr size=1> Min hit is actually: 1 + Bonus + int(dmg/10) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umemnenthmoondust.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Memnenth Moondust</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1062<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/19/02 12:52:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=247.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Damage Calculator question</span><hr size=1> SoD proc is great... for warriors... cos it grabs ALOT of aggro.<br><br>If you are counting on procs for damage youll be sadly disappointed, I thought most of us learned this with our ghoulbanes in our 30s. <p><center><a href=http://www.fallenalliance.org><img src=http://spin.emich.edu/sig/mem2.jpg><br><a href=http://www.fallenalliance.org/scripts/members/profile.pl?who=Memnenth>Equipment that makes me look like a bard</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urilkar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rilkar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 59<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/19/02 2:15:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=247.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.users.qwest.net/~user35521/Rilkar.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Damage Calculator question</span><hr size=1> Luthair is correct about the min hit.  But I figured dmg/10 is  usually small, and I was just trying to show a fast way to make a rough estimate.<br><br> - Rilkar <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umrbone1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MrBone1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 127<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/19/02 3:27:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=247.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Damage Calculator question</span><hr size=1> Do you even own a one handed weapon?  Everyone knows all one handed weapons at level 60 have a damage bonus of 11 regardless of delay... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=247.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=247.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=247.topic&index=10><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif bor